Project 2
Email Application

Scenario: You are an IT Support Administrator Specialist and are charge with the task of creating 
email accounts of new hires.

Your application should do the following:
- Generate the email with the following syntax:firstname.lastname@department.company.com
- Determine the department(scales,development,accounting)if none leave blank.
- Generate a random String for a password.
- Have set methods to change the password, set the mailbox capacity, and define a alternate email addresss 
- Have get methods to display the name , email ,and mailbox capacity